1.1.1.1
log
@
Import p5-Test-MockSleep a module to override perl's sleep
ok sthen@@

Test::MockSleep overrides perl's sleep call. A call to sleep will
not really sleep.

It also provides a facility to check how many seconds a program
would have slept.
@
text
